'''Mukulaal''' ama '''Bisad''', ({{lang-ar|قط}} {{lang-la|feles ''ama'' felis}} {{lang-it|gatto}} {{lang-en|cat}} {{lang-am|ድመት}}) waa [[xayawaan]] yar oo [[gurijoog]]to ah, taas oo cunta [[hilib]]ka, [[caano|caanaha]] iyo [[cunto]]da kale ee [[dad]]ku karsadaan. 

Mukulaasha waxeyna ka tirsan [[Bahda Bisada]], sida: [[shabeel]]ka, guduudanaha, [[libaax]]a iyo [[Haramcad|harimacadka]].

Mukulaasha waa xayawaan aad u degen oo maskiin ah. Sidoo kale waxay ka mid tahay xayawaanka [[naasley]]da ah ee ilmaheeda nuujiya. 

Yaanyuur, waxeey ku nooshahay, aduunka oo dhan.

